    <div class="container">
        <h1>How to Request Materials</h1>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8">
          
            <h2 id="searching">Searching in ArchivesSpace</h2><br>
            <p>Requesting for manuscripts and archives collections are managed through ArchivesSpace. If you are searching for book materials, please visit the Emory <a href="https://search.libraries.emory.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Library Search interface</a>.</p><br>
            <p>ArchivesSpace provides a centralized search interface for archival and manuscript collections held by the <a href="https://libraries.emory.edu/rose" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stuart A. Rose Manuscript, Archives, and Rare Book Library</a>, the <a href="https://libraries.emory.edu/rose/collections/emory-university-archives" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emory University Archives</a>, <a href="https://library.law.emory.edu/collections/archives-and-rare-books.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emory Law Archives</a>, <a href="https://oxford.library.emory.edu/special-collections" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Oxford College Archives</a>, <a href="https://pitts.emory.edu/collections/special-collections/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pitts Theology Library Special Collections and Archives</a>, and <a href="https://libraries.emory.edu/health/using-library/historical-collections" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Woodruff Health Sciences Center Library Historical Collections</a>.</p><br>
            <p>A reminder that ArchivesSpace searches words and phrases used in the finding aids that describe collections, not the words and phrases that appear in documents in the collections themselves. Although some of Emory’s collections are available digitally, access to most archival and manuscript material requires visiting our reading rooms in-person.</p><br>
          
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <nav role="navigation" class="aspace-sidebar-menu">
              <span class="sidebar-header">Requesting Menu</span>
              <ul class="links">
                <li class="link-item"><a class="link"  href="#searching">Searching For Materials</a></li>
